cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on improving the robustness of Deep Neural Networks against adversarial attacks in image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper deals with security and vulnerability of DNNs, it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
